39 4. Develop a rubric and set forth a satisfactory score to
40 determine if a pupil meets the requirements for a satisfactory score
41 in citizenship for the purposes of NRS 388.5935.
42 5. Set forth the requirements for completing a service
43 learning project for the purposes of NRS 388.5935.
